Ayesha is a gardener in Al-Kharid. She supervises the local cactus patch and will keep any seeds planted there disease-free for a payment of farming produce.

Shop[edit | edit source]

Ayesha also sells basic farming tools, which can be accessed by talking to her and asking Can you sell me something? It is not an actual shop and it has no set stock; each item has to be bought individually through the dialogue.

Changes[edit | edit source]

Date Changes
22 November 2018
(update)

Gardeners at farming patches now sell plant pots.

Trivia[edit | edit source]

  • Ayesha (عائشة) is a feminine Arabic name, meaning alive.
  • While Ayesha is a member of Group of Advanced Gardeners, she can not be used for the quest Fairy Tale I - Growing Pains.
